<h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-8">Production deployment guidance</h2>

<div class="ndx-production-section">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Ready to deploy IoT sensors in your real car parks? Here's the roadmap:
  </p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Phase 1: Pilot (1 car park, 3 months)</h3>
  <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-!-font-size-19">
    <li>
      <strong>Procure hardware:</strong> 50 ultrasonic sensors (~£6,000), 1 LoRaWAN gateway (~£400),
      installation labor (~£2,000) = £8,400 total
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Deploy AWS infrastructure:</strong> Use CloudFormation template from this walkthrough
      as baseline, customize for your needs
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Install sensors:</strong> Mount above each parking space, connect to LoRaWAN gateway,
      test connectivity
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Integrate with existing systems:</strong> Website widget showing real-time availability,
      mobile app API integration
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Monitor for 3 months:</strong> Validate sensor accuracy, measure occupancy improvements,
      calculate actual ROI
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-4">Phase 2: Scale (remaining car parks, 6 months)</h3>
  <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-!-font-size-19">
    <li>
      Present pilot results to decision-makers with ROI data
    </li>
    <li>
      Procure sensors for remaining car parks (bulk discount available)
    </li>
    <li>
      Roll out in waves (2-3 car parks per month) to manage installation workload
    </li>
    <li>
      Centralize monitoring: Single CloudWatch dashboard for all council car parks
    </li>
    <li>
      Optimize pricing and signage based on multi-car park data patterns
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-4">Phase 3: Expand (other IoT use cases, 12 months)</h3>
  <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-!-font-size-19">
    <li>
      Leverage same AWS IoT Core infrastructure for waste management sensors
    </li>
    <li>
      Add street lighting monitoring and adaptive dimming
    </li>
    <li>
      Deploy air quality sensors at strategic locations
    </li>
    <li>
      Implement flood detection in drainage systems
    </li>
    <li>
      Build unified smart city dashboard showing all IoT data streams
    </li>
  </ol>

  <div class="govuk-warning-text govuk-!-margin-top-4">
    <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
    <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
      <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
      Start with pilot before full rollout. Validate ROI assumptions, test sensor accuracy, and
      gain operational experience with small-scale deployment first.
    </strong>
  </div>
</div>

